<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>143</hymn_number>
<title>THERE'LL BE NO DARK VALLEY</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Thimna um ta puona, Isu hung tieng (3)
 A hehpihte puikhawm di'n.

[V2]
 A hehpihte puikhawm di'n (2)
 Thimna um ta puona, Isu hung tieng,
 A hehpihte puikhawm di'n.

[V3]
 2. Lungkham um ta puona Isu hung tieng (2)
 Zing vak lopi um ding, Isu hung tieng;
 A hehpihte puikhawm di'n.

[V4]
 3. Kahna um ta puona Isu hung tieng (2)
 Lakkhawmna nuom um ding, Isu hung tieng;
 A hehpihte puikhawm di'n.

[V5]
 4. Chibai buk la saitiu, Isu hung tieng (2)
 Kikhawpna nuom um ding, Isu hung tieng;
 A hehpihte puikhawm di'n.</lyrics>
</song>